3 Schlafzimmer, 5 Badezimmer. Garten 3500 m² mit Bäumen, Weinreben,...

Haven of peace, ideal for family vacations. Spacious farmhouse, everyone can preserve his privacy. Warm living room of 65 m².
3 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms. Garden 3500 m² with trees, trellis,...
